    dc:creator "Langley, Jethro; Cornwall, Morgan; Powell, Chanté; Costa, Carlo; Allsopp, Elleunorah; Noort, Simon Van; Guilbert, Eric; Asch, Barbara Van" ;
    dc:title "Tingidae Laporte 1833" ;
    trt:augmentsTaxonConcept <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Tingidae_Laporte_1833> ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4722.5.3> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4722.5.3>
    bibo:endPage "462" ;
    bibo:issue "5" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2020-01-16" ;
    bibo:startPage "443" ;
    bibo:volume "4722" ;
    dc:creator "Langley, Jethro; Cornwall, Morgan; Powell, Chanté; Costa, Carlo; Allsopp, Elleunorah; Noort, Simon Van; Guilbert, Eric; Asch, Barbara Van" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "First report of the lace bug Neoplerochila paliatseasi (Rodrigues, 1981) (Hemiptera Tingidae) infesting cultivated olive trees in South Africa, and its complete mitochondrial sequence" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3609696> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3609696>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Phylogenetic relationships among 15 lace bug species (Hemiptera: Tingidae) based on 13 mitochondrial proteincoding genes, using Bayesian inference. PCG123 was constructed using DNA sequences with partitioned codon positions. PCG12 was constructed using DNA sequences, excluding the 3rd codon position. AA was constructed using amino acid sequences. Trees were rooted by the outgroups Adelphocoris fasciaticollis and Apolygus lucorum (Miridae). Nodal statistical support is given as Bayesian posterior probability." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3609696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

